body.p:
If you define a bookmap with appendices and some
        appendix, you may want the parent
        appendices on a separate page than its children. This is done
      automatically if the bookmap contains part but if not, you may need
      to use the following
      CSS:*[topicrefclass ~= "bookmap/appendix"]:first-of-type {
  page-break-before: always;
}
